{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f2cb78bb42","title":"诗五篇","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9783304397","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"f2cb78bb42"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5dafc21bd9","name":"花月初"},{"id":"8aff656cc4","name":"上海第一师范学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d0f24cac0c","type":"title","text":"诗五篇","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"9b64028a8b","type":"authors","text":"上海第一师范学院花月初","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"c7957adf2a","type":"subtitle","text":"[花月初：中文科21班学生]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"4988366162","type":"subtitle","text":"1.天骂篇","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"27f5c07246","type":"paragraph","text":"[原编者按：花月初说，这篇诗写在生流行性感冒时，当时春雨连绵，必有感触，又想到和平解放台湾政策提出后，蒋介石还执迷不悟，不幡然归来，故作文骂之。但是，我们细看全文，有哪段能说明有这种意思的呢？我们说全篇充满了一种委曲、怨恨、反抗的情感，委曲的是自己，怨恨和反抗的是我们的党、政府、干部和各种积极分子。如果针对蒋介石而言，那么这篇诗又充满了对蒋介石的同情和希望。现在，我们把它刊登出来，请大家来嗅一嗅。]","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"c25bacdcc8","type":"paragraph","text":"呵，天！我要骂你！","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"79227c43c6","type":"paragraph","text":"骂你胡涂","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"3a1a115552","type":"paragraph","text":"骂你荒唐","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"1790e4f528","type":"paragraph","text":"骂你，骂你的无情……。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"ff6a06fd0d","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"60338b4c43","type":"paragraph","text":"我骂你荒唐——","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"02e33a5783","type":"paragraph","text":"你野蛮地拖留过春光，","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"a4bd7a61ad","type":"paragraph","text":"你将百花幽禁在深殿，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"ca9d0294b4","type":"paragraph","text":"你叫冬魔霸占了世界。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"e7b5087572","type":"paragraph","text":"要不是人们的继次的催促，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"9985199460","type":"paragraph","text":"以及春神她自己的挣脱，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"fcf67d4368","type":"paragraph","text":"谁知她能否回到人间。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"524a84b00b","type":"paragraph","text":"年年都是如此，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"c38a6269e8","type":"paragraph","text":"谁知你安的是什么心眼。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"4df9eb04c4","type":"paragraph","text":"你难道一点也不明白，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"8a7e29825b","type":"paragraph","text":"花园里最欢迎的只是春天？!","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"a81fd6b087","type":"paragraph","text":"我骂你无情——","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"fe56d7118d","type":"paragraph","text":"你忘尽了人们给你的恩典。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"7a770e402b","type":"paragraph","text":"早在难以查考的年代，","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"5fd8440a99","type":"paragraph","text":"善良的人们唤醒了你的沉眠；","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"c78cdbb2dc","type":"paragraph","text":"五千年前一个遗忘了的日子，","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"958f0c2a28","type":"paragraph","text":"共工氏触了“不周之山”，","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"1b80fecb34","type":"paragraph","text":"你受伤了，满脸布着昏暗，","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"3bf2a9ce15","type":"paragraph","text":"多亏了※的热肠，","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"256c64c38a","type":"paragraph","text":"耐心地给你治伤。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"1cb850e561","type":"paragraph","text":"你好了，长大了，于是忘记了这一切!","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"8e82911936","type":"paragraph","text":"于是，你怂慂风暴猖獗，","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"28a8d0ce7d","type":"paragraph","text":"你掀动江河泛滥。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"49ce5710f5","type":"paragraph","text":"冬日，你拼命吸收大地的热力，","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"b189e9a75f","type":"paragraph","text":"夏天，你又喷吐干旱的火焰。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"96a5125840","type":"paragraph","text":"你驱使了无数病魔，","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"b4ed5afe5f","type":"paragraph","text":"任它们放肆、扰窜……。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"8fc69b4ef6","type":"paragraph","text":"这是为表示你一点点“尊严”？","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"5c820f3a52","type":"paragraph","text":"还是想告诉人们说你是不可侵犯？","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"bc64549a79","type":"paragraph","text":"不，不这些无非是证明了你的忘情。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"8f2327e67b","type":"paragraph","text":"以及可怜可恶的傲慢。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"1bc414d115","type":"paragraph","text":"我骂你糊涂——","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"e35c8eb19d","type":"paragraph","text":"你撒下了种种手段。","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"4cc4c8f590","type":"paragraph","text":"企图达到你卑鄙的心愿。","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"e631e7ccdb","type":"paragraph","text":"果然，有时你也确是十分诱人，","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"80776bb2f2","type":"paragraph","text":"你显得那么透明，那么碧蓝；","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"272b3bb8f9","type":"paragraph","text":"你也曾为人们做过一些好事，","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"f401bd0fad","type":"paragraph","text":"然而，这不值得挂在口上夸谈，","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"9963e7b8bf","type":"paragraph","text":"那不过是你底本能、义务和责任。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"20625376b6","type":"paragraph","text":"告诉你，莫再孤高自赏，","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"4dd8b1ce99","type":"paragraph","text":"睁开眼睛看看今天的下界。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"88b3cadc88","type":"paragraph","text":"看见了么？那泛起红光的地方，","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"66d4a9c372","type":"paragraph","text":"有多少支智慧的宝剑，","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"7322bd868b","type":"paragraph","text":"它们脱鞘而出，闪闪发光。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"492c01e635","type":"paragraph","text":"如果为了需要，","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"608a536f00","type":"paragraph","text":"它们马上可以戳破你的虚伪，","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"57721f8b5f","type":"paragraph","text":"你的无力和你的残暴。","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"5b2172e1ee","type":"paragraph","text":"别以为他们是如何渺小，","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"fbb7f09094","type":"paragraph","text":"岂不知你自己就是它们所造。","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"72fb549cdd","type":"paragraph","text":"他们授予我，诗人的口舌以力量。","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"fe18e0d897","type":"paragraph","text":"我责骂你，然而也同情你","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"db7457e31d","type":"paragraph","text":"只要——","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"0074109f38","type":"paragraph","text":"你愿真心地皈依在真理的门下，","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"ed5636e267","type":"paragraph","text":"然而，这也是你唯一的正道。","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"7915b2bcc5","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"e82438023a","type":"paragraph","text":"起风吧！轰雷吧！注雨吧！叫吧！","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"5f4aa64d1b","type":"paragraph","text":"医治你混身的疮斑，","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"189a4c9ce5","type":"paragraph","text":"吐尽你满腹的愚昧，","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"e2ce80d56c","type":"paragraph","text":"争取复元的那天，","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"42bd0ecf81","type":"paragraph","text":"用你诚恳的忏悟和眼泪……。","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"64b46fc4d3","type":"paragraph","text":"中文科21班花月初","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"692c922c02","type":"subtitle","text":"2.哀歌--迎月有感漫成一绝","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"047d2d115e","type":"paragraph","text":"银色蟾光何皎皎？万缕郁×心头×。","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f2cb78bb42"},{"id":"f6d28d6b81","type":"paragraph","text":"庭前黄叶飘飘下，仰观秋空归旧朝。","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f